seo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-6f5","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":23955,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/10\/31\/abu-darda-reconciliation\/","url_meta":{"origin":23999,"position":0},"title":"Abu Darda on Virtue: No deeds better than prayer, good character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 31, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Idris reported: Abu Darda, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cNo deeds of the children of Adam are better than walking to prayer, having exceptional character, and reconciling people.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd wal-Raqa\u0304\u2019iq 725 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0625\u0650\u062f\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0633\u064e \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0623\u0628\u0648 \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0631\u062f\u0627\u0621 \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0650\u0644\u064e \u0622\u062f\u064e\u0645\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064c \u0639\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0644\u064b\u0627 \u062e\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064b\u0627 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6068,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/08\/islah-dhat-bayn-better\/","url_meta":{"origin":23999,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Reconciliation: Good relations better than voluntary worship","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 8, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cShall I not tell you of what is better in degree than extra fasts, prayers, and charity?\u201d They said, \"Of course!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cReconciliation between people, for ruined relations between people is the razor.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43395,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/22\/pleased-by-reconciliation\/","url_meta":{"origin":23999,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Peacemaking: Allah and His Messenger pleased by reconciliation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 22, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ayyub reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Abu Ayyub! Shall I not tell you of a deed most pleasing to Allah and His Messenger?\u201d He said, \u201cOf course!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThat you reconcile people when there is resentment between them, and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22466,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/04\/07\/loves-islah-bayna-nas\/","url_meta":{"origin":23999,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Peacemaking: Allah and His Messenger love reconciliation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 7, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ayyub reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cShall I not tell you of a charity beloved to Allah and His Messenger? That you reconcile people when there is hatred and resentment between them.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 3922 Grade: Hasan li ghayrihi (fair\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8711,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/23\/hilm-good-akhlaq-wrong-you\/","url_meta":{"origin":23999,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Forbearance: Be good to those who are evil to you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 23, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best of virtues is that you maintain relations with one who cuts you off, that you give to one who deprives you, and that you forgive one who insults you.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 15618\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":882,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/06\/22\/all-good-deeds-are-rewarded\/","url_meta":{"origin":23999,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Charity: All good deeds rewarded, even smiling","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 22, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not belittle any good deed, even meeting your brother with a cheerful face.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2626 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0630\u064e\u0631\u064d\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u06